Title: Burden of Proof
Plot: Grissom investigates the murder of a Las Vegas photographer whose remains were dumped at a nearby body farm where CSIs routinely study corpses, and his findings reveal that the man was apparently shot to death even though there are no bullet fragments in the body.
GuestStars: Janet Gunn, Sara Paxton, Dan Byrd, Nancy Valen, Monnae Michaell, Jason Beghe, Patrick Tomas O'Brien, David Sobel, John Rosenfeld, Roger Hamilton
